{"tid":2463590,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港台：至今約5600名市民已接種第二劑科興疫苗","createTime":"2021-03-26T22:14:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-26T22:17:08.000Z","uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"955b77710eb78815c14d6a14528c9faa50560ac7","tid":2463590,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T22:14:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n新冠疫苗接種計劃開展第29日，政府表示，已為市民接種超過43萬5千劑疫苗。約5600名市民已接種第二劑科興疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n42萬9500名市民已接種第一劑疫苗，當中27萬8200人接種科興疫苗，15萬1300人接種復必泰疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>另外，過去24小時並沒有接種疫苗後的送院個案。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1582835-20210326.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1582835-20210326.htm&d=qOmKSCuv03M2cFfeadZVWoMY%2BwsNvTr2Nz54cwdIBJg%3D&h=93756102\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1582835-20210326.htm&h=7c73234d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1582835-20210326.htm</a>"},{"pid":"a105aaa86b2849ee2c45b67e13d044564de442f7","tid":2463590,"uid":186431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T22:17:08.000Z","msg":"要打第三劑先會有效的<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}